{
  "stem": "3360.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my mother's older sister and her husband, who had no children, took me in while my mother had a very serious operation.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- so it was also one of the most wonderful times in my life.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There wasn't a place that my aunt went that she didn't take me along.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She went to, she went to play bridge.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She went to little parties.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And always, these people would have some little extra thing for me, like a little, a couple of little chocolate bars tied together, or a little cup, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was just wonderful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And her neighbors were just wonderful people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And what I remember there is, on various occasions, the style was, in Germany-- it probably still is nowadays, perhaps not as much-- to come home at noon or one o'clock and eat your midday meal, which is your bigger meal.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my uncle, my uncle, Robert, Robert Brandt, would come home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And on various occasions, he would have in tow a beggar from the streets of Berlin that he had brought-- excuse me-- brought up to the apartment.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And my aunt was not very enthusiastic about it, but she sat down and, and set a place for him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he ate.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He had a meal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so, that was-- and that also shows you'd you how good these people were.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They were, they were just utterly and totally fine and good people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, my father was a-- [CLEARING THROAT] Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father actually sold advertising in magazines.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my, my early religious training, well, let's say it was practically nil.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
